QuestData.Title: A Witness to History
QuestData.Description: I will gather up the other Tauren pilgrims and we will travel into the Vale together.$b$bMeet me at the Gate of the August Celestials at the southern edge of Kun-Lai Summit and speak with me there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Sunwalker Dezco at the Gate of the August Celestials.

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Dezco at the Gate of the August Celestials
